		<hr size="1">Find an undead thing that cons dark blue.  Cast Spook the Dead on it.  Chase it hitting it until it dies.</P><P>Or</P><P>Find a live thing that cons dark blue.  Use Cancel Magic to pull it so you have a shot at dropping any potential damage shield it may have.  Cast Root on it and keep it rooted so you can back off and heal if necessary.  Cast Flash of Light to reduce the damage it does to you.  Stand there and hit it until it dies.</P><P>That's pretty much it, no matter what level you are. </P><P></P><P><img src="http://homepages.paradise.net.nz/vikkibri/NDKohi.JPG" width=90 align=left><font face="Castellar,CenturySchoolbook,Arial" size="+1" color="CornflowerBlue"><b>Be strong<BR>Walk tall<BR>Go with pride</b></font><BR><a HREF="http://www.serenity-within.com/View_Member.php?Name=Kohinoor">Kohinoor Noblespirit of Felwithe</a><BR><a HREF="http://www.serenity-within.com">Serenity Within Guild</a></P><P>55th Crusade</P><P><a HREF="http://www.purenz.com/?98B94218-FEC9-430A-8CEF-AB2A52EAFCE1">New Zealand, home of Middle-Earth</a></font><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
